# Project-local signals live here. Two valid file types:
#
# 1. Project-specific signal modules (plain Python files) — only used by this
#    project. Edit freely.
#
# 2. SYMLINKS to reusable signals in `MyProjects/shared/signals/`. Create with:
#       ln -s ../../../shared/signals/my_signal.py domain/signals/my_signal.py
#    (THREE `..` — targets resolve relative to the symlink's location.)
#    Edit the shared source, NEVER the link.
#
# See MyProjects/shared/README.md and workspace AGENTS.md § "Using Shared Signals".
